WEBVTT

00:02.994 --> 00:04.244
WOMAN: Previously, on "Freakish"...

00:04.245 --> 00:05.898
Stay strong.

00:06.979 --> 00:09.023
- Good luck, man.
- Let's do it.

00:10.327 --> 00:12.778
John Collins. Rescue and Recovery.

00:12.779 --> 00:14.071
We leave in five minutes.

00:14.072 --> 00:16.532
- BOTH: [laugh, exhale]
- We have a vaccine.

00:16.533 --> 00:18.576
All of you happen to believe a man

00:18.577 --> 00:21.579
who has a suitcase full
of shots which are all poison.

00:21.580 --> 00:24.331
- How long have we been out?
- Couple minutes, I think.

00:24.332 --> 00:25.583
What does he want from us?

00:25.584 --> 00:26.834
Just a pinch.

00:26.835 --> 00:28.627
Okay.

00:28.628 --> 00:32.590
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

00:32.591 --> 00:33.966
[grunts]

00:33.967 --> 00:36.218
I can't break free.

00:36.842 --> 00:38.460
I know how to do this.

00:38.764 --> 00:40.506
Uhh!

00:40.531 --> 00:43.200
I guess... you saw that in a movie once.

00:45.187 --> 00:46.438
Uhh...

00:50.233 --> 00:51.901
I'm not a fan of needles.

00:51.902 --> 00:53.191
Nobody is.

00:53.695 --> 00:56.739
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:56.740 --> 00:58.824
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:58.825 --> 01:00.075
Something wrong?

01:00.076 --> 01:01.244
- [thud]
- Uhh!

01:02.454 --> 01:04.413
Why did you do that?

01:04.414 --> 01:06.207
It's not a vaccine.

01:06.208 --> 01:08.417
It's a poison. He's here to kill us.

01:09.761 --> 01:11.300
It's a poison?

01:12.172 --> 01:15.216
<i>[tense music]</i>

01:15.241 --> 01:20.496
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:25.602 --> 01:27.895
Two aspirin would kill a guinea pig.

01:28.344 --> 01:30.282
So could a shot of vodka.

01:30.440 --> 01:32.066
Or a cup of mouthwash.

01:32.067 --> 01:34.860
I didn't give it even close
to the full dosage.

01:34.885 --> 01:37.005
What did you put in my body?

01:37.030 --> 01:39.949
A vaccine. To protect you.

01:39.950 --> 01:41.575
How do you feel?

01:41.576 --> 01:43.118
Fine.

01:43.119 --> 01:45.371
I mean, my stomach's
a little weird, but...

01:45.372 --> 01:47.039
I think it's just nerves.

01:47.064 --> 01:49.572
- He tied me up.
- Because you and your friends

01:49.597 --> 01:51.126
blew up the chemical plant.

01:51.127 --> 01:52.963
But why did you knock me out?

01:54.297 --> 01:56.590
- Diesel?
- It's pretty simple.

01:57.136 --> 01:59.702
You're saying this is a vaccine, right?

02:02.055 --> 02:04.375
Well, that means you wouldn't
mind getting, now, would you?

02:05.433 --> 02:08.561
<i>[tense music]</i>

02:08.562 --> 02:14.650
<i>♪ ♪</i>

02:14.651 --> 02:15.985
Don't.

02:15.986 --> 02:17.028
[exhales]

02:19.614 --> 02:21.481
[panting]

02:22.810 --> 02:24.496
Why are you trying to kill us?

02:25.203 --> 02:27.204
I'm doin' my job.

02:27.205 --> 02:28.914
It's because we're witnesses

02:28.915 --> 02:30.541
to the horror show going on out there.

02:30.542 --> 02:33.669
All I know is... your friend
doesn't have to die.

02:33.670 --> 02:37.131
What's in the syringe?
What kind of poison is it?

02:37.132 --> 02:39.258
- I don't know.
- Unlikely.

02:39.259 --> 02:41.988
Her only chance
is getting medical attention.

02:42.304 --> 02:44.221
- I can radio for help.
- Sure.

02:44.660 --> 02:46.974
Right after you call for
more people to come kill us.

02:46.999 --> 02:48.475
Then send me to my vehicle.

02:49.050 --> 02:51.061
I have an extra suit.
I can get her outta here.

02:51.062 --> 02:53.564
You'll go get it and come
back, just to be nice?

02:53.565 --> 02:55.357
She'll die if you don't trust me.

02:55.358 --> 02:57.902
She's dying because we did trust you.

02:57.927 --> 02:59.444
Yeah, well, she's not dying alone.

03:00.363 --> 03:03.407
<i>[dramatic musical build‐up]</i>

03:03.408 --> 03:05.700
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:05.701 --> 03:06.943
<i>[eerie music]</i>

